						<p align="center"><span style="mso-fareast-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA"><font style="font-family: 'sans-serif';font-style:Normal;font-size: small; color: #000000;"><b><a name="CHAPTER V">CHAPTER 
											V</a></b></font></span></p>
					</font>
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td valign="top" align="center" colspan="5" height="20"><font style="font-family: 'sans-serif';font-style:Normal;font-size: small; color: #000000;"><span style="FONT-WEIGHT: 700; TEXT-DECORATION: underline; mso-fareast-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">OFFICERS</span></font></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td valign="top" align="center" height="20"><font style="font-family: 'sans-serif';font-style:Normal;font-size: small; color: #000000;"><span style="FONT-WEIGHT: 700; mso-fareast-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-bidi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">32.</span></font></td>
            <td valign="top" colspan="4" height="20"><font style="font-family: 'sans-serif';font-style:Normal;font-size: small; color: #000000;"><span style="mso-fareast-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-bidi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA"><u>Designation.</u> – 
      </span></font></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td valign="top" align="center" height="60">&nbsp;</td>
            <td valign="top" colspan="4" height="60"><font style="font-family: 'sans-serif';font-style:Normal;font-size: small; color: #000000;"><span style="mso-fareast-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-bidi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 
      The principal officers of the Association shall be a President, a 
      Vice-president, a Secretary and a Treasurer, all of whom shall be elected 
      by and<span style="mso-fareast-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">&nbsp; </span>from the Board of Managers. The Board 
      may appoint an Assistant Treasurer, and a Assistant Secretary and 
      such<span style="mso-fareast-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">&nbsp; </span>other officers as in their judgment may 
      be necessary ( in the case of an Association of one hundred<span style="mso-fareast-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">&nbsp; </span>owners<span style="mso-fareast-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">&nbsp; </span>or less the offices<span style="mso-fareast-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">&nbsp; </span>of treasurer and Secretary may be 
      filled by the same person).</span></font></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td valign="top" align="center" height="20"><font style="font-family: 'sans-serif';font-style:Normal;font-size: small; color: #000000;"><span style="FONT-WEIGHT: 700; mso-fareast-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA"><font style="font-family: 'sans-serif';font-style:Normal;font-size: small; color: #000000;">33.</font></span></font></td>
